title: Jules Thin Crust Pizza
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Organic, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Counter service pizza restaurant making thin crust pizza and organic salads. The flour and tomato sauce are organic. Offers gluten-free crust (contains eggs) and whole wheat crust (contains honey). All dressings contain honey or worcestershire sauce. Around 15 veg toppings combinations, 2 dairy-free. Ask for Daiya vegan cheese.
